snippet.title: Diana and Roma at School - A Story about the Value of Friendship
snippet.description:
Diana and her school friend have different situations at school, pleasant and not so. But thanks to them, they realize the values ​​of friendship and the fact that a friend is known not only in joy. A story about the value of friendship.
Thanks for watching!
